<p>Lens will automatically create this settings file for you when you first run Lens.
But feel free to change any of the settings!</p>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="src">src</dt>
	<dd>The path to your <:link "src" "reference/organization/src":> directory, relative to the project root.</dd>
</dl>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="autoload">autoload</dt>
	<dd>The path to your “<a href="/reference/organization/lens/autoload.php/">autoload.php</a>” file, relative to the project root.</dd>
</dl>
